pesticide.PPE: long-sleeved shirt and long pants, and shoes plus socks

Active_Ingredients.name: Glyphosate
Active_Ingredients.mode_Of_Action: Inhibits an enzyme found only in plants and microorganisms that is essential to formation of specific amino acids

Safety_Information.general_Info: Remove and wash contaminated clothing before reuse. Relatively nontoxic to dogs and other domestic animals; ingestion may result in temporary gastrointestinal irritation such as vomiting, diarrhea, colic. Provide fluids to prevent dehydration.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: In case of an emergency involving this herbicide product, or for medical assistance, call (800) 262-8200.
